desc_long									Radial Impact Available Through Unreal Engine 4									You can find Radial Impact available through the Learning Tab of the Unreal Engine 4 Launcher for free download so that you can learn how I made the game!																						关于这款游戏							Radial Impact is a fast-paced, single-player game that challenges players’ reflexes by matching the sizes of two circles; one static and one dynamic.Game Features:Single-Player.Multiple Game Modes (Classic, Time Trial, and Waves).Simple Mechanics (Click to Interact).Dynamic Circle Sizes and Locations.Developed solely by Devin Sherry.Classic Mode – OverviewGame-play focused on getting the highest score.Points earned based on how close the player matches the shape of the circles.Three Lives – Once all lives are lost, the player loses and the game ends.Slow-down ability unlocked if the player gets a Perfect rating 5x in a row.If the player reaches a 10X Perfect multiplier, they earn back a life if one was lost.Lives are lost if the player gets either a Bad or a Miss rating.Saved Data for High Score.https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TptSCxxTkosTime Trial – OverviewGame-play focused on lasting the longest without time running out.Time is added and subtracted based on how close the player matches the shape of the circles.The player starts with 59 seconds until the game ends.Slow-down ability unlocked if the player gets a Perfect rating 5x in a row.Saved Data for Longest Time.https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BwH2Q-p2m9sWaves Mode – OverviewThe goal of the player is to earn a score that is larger than the “Score to Beat” for each waves option and set there own high score.There are multiple “Waves” options for the player to choose from. There are 5 Waves, 10 Waves, 25 Waves, and 50 Waves.A “Wave” consists of one turn of the player matching the two circles shapes.At the start, only the “5 Waves” mode is unlocked for the player. As the player scores higher than the “Score to Beat” the player will unlock the higher waves options.Slow-down ability unlocked if the player gets a Perfect rating 5x in a row.Saved Data to track which waves options have been unlocked.https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zs3Na0Vg0x8						
